  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Tazarotene Gel in Nail Psoriasis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Trial to Evaluate the Anti-psoriatic Efficacy and Tolerability of Tazarotene in a Gel Formulation in Patients With Mild to Moderate Nail Psoriasis - Parallel Group Comparison</official_title>
